Subject: Unable to Uninstall EPP client from machine.
Description:
We are trying to uninstall EPP client through EPP uninstaller script.
Uninstaller script is stuck at 'No product code was found' and does not get completed. EPP is not found in control panel however EPP icon is visible in System Tray. Also in EPP console the machine is shown as Licensed & connected, please help in clean uninstallation of EPP client from machine.
Solution_Comment__c: Customer confirmed that the case is solved now by running the tool and restarting the system afterwards.
